      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled caliber. This specimen has been curated to an exacting standard, exhibiting showroom-level integrity both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship, offering the most demanding enthusiast an opportunity to acquire a motorcar in peerless condition. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who accept nothing less than perfection.",
