    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person! It is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it honestly looks and drives like it just came off the lot. It\u2019s a total dream on the road and I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
